profile: At Roofco we offer a wide variety of installation and maintenance services, from Flat Roofs, Metal Roofs, Sloped/Pitched Roofs and Green Roofs, to Blown-In Insulation, Seamless Eavestroughs (Gutters), Facia Covers and Soffits. Located in Parksville and serving Vancouver Island and the greater BC area, our trained and fully insured team is always ready to help with your roofing needs. Feel free to Contact Us at any time to chat about how we can help you.
